{"tid":1577961,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"躲避警方搜查，無人機救走電腦硬碟","createTime":"2019-09-18T02:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:01:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2574ab7be56da761701c90bbf539c7fe790370d1","tid":1577961,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"躲避警方搜查，無人機救走電腦硬碟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/09/18/russian-police-raid/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F18%2Frussian-police-raid%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5LTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=cc90e345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2019/09/18/russian-police-raid/</a><br />\n<br />\n置身在警察國家，任何人都可能遭隨意安插罪名，入屋搜查。日前俄羅斯警方以調查洗黑錢為名，大舉搜查異見人士住所，有反對派領袖為保重要資料不會落入政府手中，於是以航拍無人機載走電腦硬碟，成功確保資料沒有外洩。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司（BBC）報道，普京為首的執政統一俄羅斯黨，在莫斯科地方選舉受重挫，反對派領袖納瓦爾尼（Alexei Navalny）號召選民策略性投票，使執政黨損失 3 分 1 議席。警方選舉後數日展開約 200 次搜捕行動，納瓦尼成為搜查行動目標，反對派地方領袖 Sergey Boyko 亦無法倖免。<br />\n<br />\n居住新西伯利亞高層公寓的 Boyko 與女友聲稱，在 9 月 12 日早上 10 時，有人猛力敲打大門，<span style=\"color: red;\">有一班面戴口罩、身穿便衣的男子自稱警察，要求入內搜證，卻又未能出示任何搜查令。<br />\n<br />\nBoyko 隨即操作航拍無人機，從單位把重要的電腦硬碟送走，還以 YouTube 直播，全程以俄語旁述。他在片段中表示：「撤離行動大功告成，無人機已經抵達目的地。」<br />\n<br />\n根據社運分子的解釋，無人機當時載有多個硬碟及記憶棒，包含「非常重要」而不能落入警方的資訊，最終送到朋友手中。門外男子隨後企圖破門入屋，Boyko 在律師協助下交涉，最終讓男子入屋搜查。</span><br />\n<br />\n普京政府以洗黑錢為名，針對納瓦爾尼的「反貪腐基金會（Anti-Corruption Foundation）」，同日在超過 40 座城市進行同類搜查。有反對派義工被警方帶走問話，電腦及手機被沒收，有部分異見分子的個人銀行帳戶被凍結，組織在新西伯利亞的總部同樣受到調查。反對派批評，所謂洗黑錢都是誣陷的冤罪，組織所得經費都是由公眾捐獻。<br />\n<br />\nBoyko 在 12 日遭搜查後翌日，其單位再次遭到警方突襲，相信是要報復他以無人機送走資料。另一名反對派領袖 Leonid Volkov 表示：「這一次行動非常蠻橫，所有東西都被查封沒收了。」"},{"pid":"f4322b4efcac314792f66a3c55491eb93588a63e","tid":1577961,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"226767d0ffe3e741bd45caff2a9ce65fa288d464","tid":1577961,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:59:57.000Z","msg":"要突破<br />\n明明香港人連航拍機都整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8083e327643ce945a442772c4de94d865a4055","tid":1577961,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed7a305999513d25f1782c61bb379a415658426","tid":1577961,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"[策略] 新兵種飛行哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9406dcb76f91b052b9bbcb9c6bc7f703578c334e","tid":1577961,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e06c58a0e79253fa3cc224789a0f138c6da5f6f","tid":1577961,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:31:32.000Z","msg":"國慶咁大件事 緊係要約埋建制議員賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605409</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGVTmzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGVTmzV.jpg&h=c9cd4e99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1af4004153b65d72e05a67d515c091ba91000024","tid":1577961,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"我地都要學呢啲技能"}]}